### ---------- for products ----------

### create a product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/product/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jollibee Phoenix",
    "description": "The best fast food in the world",
    "price": 4000,
    "discount": 25,
    "image": "https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/1x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png",
    "status": "In Stock",
    "category": "Food"
}
###


### delete a product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/product/delete/Iphone 16 Pro Max
###


### get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/getAll
###


### update a product availability
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/product/update/availability/Biriyani
###


### update a product description
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/product/update/description/Iphone 16 Pro Max
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "The latest Iphone 16 Pro Max - The best phone ever?"
}
###


### update a product discount
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/product/update/discount/Jollibee Phoenix/15
###


### filter products by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/filter/category/Food
###


### filter products by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/filter/name/pHo
###